"<li style=\" font-size:11pt;\" style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:700;\">Network Modeling</span>: NeTrainSim allows you to model entire rail networks, enabling simulations at different scales, from local segments to country-wide networks.</li>\n"
