"<li style=\" font-size:11pt;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:700;\">Versatility and Adaptability</span>: NeTrainSim supports various rail network types and configurations, allowing you to customize and adapt the simulation according to your specific needs.</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-size:11pt;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-weight:700;\">Open-Source Development</span>: NeTrainSim is an open-source project, promoting collaboration, innovation, and customization for researchers and developers.</li>\n"
